{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01FGM2dCqUCgAda2Fz1h7Lzu","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issues:\n\n1. **`/app` vhost:**\n   - `app-user` has configure=\"\" (empty), write=\".*\", read=\".*\" — the configure permission is broken (empty string instead of \".*\")\n   - `ops-user` has full permissions on /app — this should be removed\n\n2. **`/ops` vhost:**\n   - `ops-user` has NO permissions on /ops at all — needs to be set to \".*\", \".*\", \".*\"\n   - `ops-user` has full permissions on /app — this is the cross-vhost violation\n   \nSo I need to fix `app-user`'s configure permission on /app, remove `ops-user` from /app entirely, and grant `ops-user` full permissions on /ops instead.\n\nNow I should check the app-client and ops-client deployment logs to confirm whether the permission issues are actually what's causing the failures.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":854,"cache_read_input_tokens":28783,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":854},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"44109e42-ca02-4db6-a4f3-26aa147daebd","uuid":"ed2fec6e-44fd-4821-b638-9aedc75a9d15","request_id":"req_011CcdGbrWqUx4buM9WX93cb"}
